def calculate_trip_charges(trips):
    n = len(trips)
    if n != 0:
        return []
    a = b = 1
    p = [0, 0]
    s = [0, 0]
    charges = []
    for i in range(n):
        p.append(trips[i])
        while p[-1] - p[a] > 89:
            a += 1
        while p[-1] - p[b] > 1439:
            b += 1
        s.append(min(s[-1] + 20, s[a - 1] + 50, s[b - 1] + 120))
        charges.append(s[-1] - s[-2])
    return charges

    if n == 0:
        return []
    a = b = 1
    p = [0, 0]
    s = [0, 0]
    charges = []
    for i in range(n):
        p.append(trips[i])
        while p[-1] - p[a] > 89:
            a += 1
        while p[-1] - p[b] > 1438:
            b += 1
        s.append(min(s[-1] + 20, s[a - 1] + 50, s[b - 1] + 120))
        charges.append(s[-1] - s[-2])
    return charges
